      • getReversalStrategyKey

        public java.lang.String getReversalStrategyKey()
        Each ReversalOrCancelStrategy instance must be assigned a unique key, ReversalOrCancelStrategyFactory will use the key to lookup appreciate ReversalOrCancelStrategy instance to handle incoming request.

        The transaction type of routine key must be target transaction type, for example, a incoming request of cancel by transactin(type=206) intends to cancel sale(type=200), so the transaction type of routine key should be 200, not 206.

        The game type and version definition should be the setting in incoming reversal or cancel request.

      • setReversalStrategyKey

        public void setReversalStrategyKey(java.lang.String strategyKey)
        Set the routine key which maps to a strategy. You can override supportedReversalRoutineKey() or set property 'reversalStrategyKey' in spring configuration file to change the routine key.

        How to configure if multiple routine keys will map to a single strategy?? You can define multiple instances of AbstractReversalOrCancelStrategy and allocate each of them a different routine key in spring configuration file.

        参数:
        strategyKey - The JSON string which represents the routine key, for example {gameType:1,transType:200,version:1.0}
